Rate limiting be damned

suppressPackageStartupMessages(library(tidyr))
## Warning: package 'tidyr' was built under R version 3.3.2
res <- new_tibble %>% 
  filter(watchers > 200) %>%
  rowwise %>% 
  mutate(contributors = contrib_url %>%
           GET %>%
           content %>%
           map_chr('login') %>%
           str_c(collapse=',')) %>%
  ungroup %>% 
  arrange(desc(watchers))
res %>% select(-watchers)
